<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body class="font-sans text-gray-800">

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hero-bg-shape top-0 right-0 translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/3 absolute"></div>
    <div class="hero-bg-shape bottom-0 left-0 -translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3 absolute"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-8 z-10" data-aos="fade-right">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 rounded-full border border-slate-200">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-sma-grey uppercase tracking-widest">Platform Akademik Terintegrasi</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight text-balance">
          Revolusi Digital <br>
          <span class="text-gradient">Rapor & Karir Siswa</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
          Menghubungkan pencapaian akademik yang nyata dengan peluang karir masa depan melalui satu ekosistem digital yang terpercaya.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/auth/login?role=siswa" class="px-8 py-4 bg-sma-grey text-white rounded-2xl font-bold text-base shadow-premium hover:bg-sma-dark hover:shadow-glow transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center">
            Login Siswa
          </a>
          <a href="/auth/login?role=guru" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-sma-grey text-sma-grey rounded-2xl font-bold text-base hover:bg-sma-grey hover:text-white transition-all text-center">
            Portal Guru
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400 pt-4">
          <div class="flex -space-x-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white bg-blue-200 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold">RP</div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white bg-green-200 flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 text-xs font-bold">AD</div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white bg-orange-200 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-700 text-xs font-bold">CK</div>
          </div>
          <p>Bergabung dengan <span class="font-bold text-sma-grey">1.000+ Siswa</span> lainnya</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 flex justify-center lg:justify-end" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-md">
          <!-- Floating Cards -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-premium p-8 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sma-grey/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-xl text-sma-grey"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Dashboard Preview</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Real-time Monitoring</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">IPK</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">3.85</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Ranking</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">#5</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 text-center">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Hadir</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-green-600">98%</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="flex-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full h-2"><div class="bg-sma-grey h-2 rounded-full w-4/5"></div></div>
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">80%</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating Verification Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-premium flex items-center gap-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-xl">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Status Dokumen</p>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-800">Terverifikasi QR</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <div id="stats" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto -mt-10 relative z-20 px-4" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-bento shadow-premium p-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 divide-y md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x divide-gray-100">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-4 md:py-0 px-4">
        <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-sma-grey mb-1">1000+</span>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Siswa Aktif</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-4 md:py-0 px-4">
        <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-sma-grey mb-1">50+</span>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Guru & Staf</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-4 md:py-0 px-4">
        <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-sma-grey mb-1">100%</span>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Keamanan Data</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-white relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 text-balance">Solusi Lengkap dalam Satu Platform</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Kami menggabungkan kemudahan administrasi guru dengan visibilitas penuh bagi siswa dan orang tua.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bento-card bg-white p-8 rounded-bento shadow-soft border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-start" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500 bg-opacity-10 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 shadow-sm">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-blue-500"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Digital Report</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Monitoring nilai siswa secara real-time. Orang tua dapat melihat perkembangan akademik anak tanpa menunggu rapor fisik.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bento-card bg-white p-8 rounded-bento shadow-soft border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-start" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-green-500 bg-opacity-10 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 shadow-sm">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-excel text-green-500"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Excel Sync</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Guru dapat memasukkan nilai dengan mudah melalui format Excel yang familiar, sistem akan otomatis menyinkronkannya.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bento-card bg-white p-8 rounded-bento shadow-soft border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-start" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500 bg-opacity-10 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 shadow-sm">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-id-card text-indigo-500"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">CV Builder</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Buat CV profesional secara otomatis berdasarkan data prestasi dan nilai akademik selama sekolah.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bento-card bg-white p-8 rounded-bento shadow-soft border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-start" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-orange-500 bg-opacity-10 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 shadow-sm">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode text-orange-500"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">QR Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Setiap dokumen rapor dan sertifikat dilengkapi QR Code unik untuk memastikan keaslian dan mencegah pemalsuan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-bg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Bagaimana Cara Kerjanya?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Proses sederhana dari input data hingga dokumen siap pakai.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-soft flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-sma-grey">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Guru Input Nilai</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Guru mengunduh template Excel, mengisi nilai offline, dan mengunggah kembali ke sistem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-soft flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-sma-grey">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Siswa Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Siswa login ke dashboard Bento Box untuk melihat grafik perkembangan nilai dan kehadiran.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-soft flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border border-gray-100">
            <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-sma-grey">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Generate Dokumen</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Unduh rapor digital terverifikasi QR dan buat CV profesional otomatis dari data akademik.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial Section -->
  <section id="testimonials" class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-bento shadow-soft p-10 lg:p-14 text-center relative border border-gray-100">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left text-6xl text-slate-200 absolute top-8 left-8"></i>

        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-700 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8 relative z-10 text-pretty">
          "E-Rapor & Career Bridge benar-benar mengubah cara kami mengelola data akademik. Proses input nilai jadi lebih cepat, dan siswa lebih termotivasi karena melihat langsung dampaknya pada CV mereka."
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-sma-grey flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">HW</div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Dr. Hendro Wibowo, M.Pd</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-sma-grey">Kepala Sekolah SMA Harapan Bangsa</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-sma-grey relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white opacity-5 rounded-full -mr-16 -mt-16 blur-2xl"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 text-balance">Siap Memulai Transformasi Digital?</h2>
      <p class="text-sma-light mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">Bergabunglah dengan ribuan sekolah yang telah menggunakan E-Rapor untuk mengelola data akademik lebih efisien.</p>
      <a href="/auth/login" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-sma-grey px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-base hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all shadow-lg">
        Mulai Sekarang <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
